Space-Conky by malbzamora: http://malbzamora.deviantart.com/

1.- You need install the fonts included
2.- Set up on the conkyrc file the correct path to "aros.lua" and "texto.lua"
3.- Set the start.sh file to be loaded on your autostart (This depends of your distro)

Thanks to wlourf for the lua/cairo scripts: http://wlourf.deviantart.com/

License: GPL3

Enjoy and improve it!
